{"tid":1729562,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"給香港抗爭青年的一封信","createTime":"2019-11-17T09:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T09:33:18.000Z","uid":24400,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f41164ce9b214e1d909ee1fea6311808043b0019","tid":1729562,"uid":24400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:25:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔係講好要be water嗎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n（一）Be Water（水聚散）不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）。<br />\n抗爭運動至今有效，因為Be Water（水聚散）的策略奏效，但從11月11日的「中文大學保衛戰」來看，港青接下來被中共設局引誘，脫離Be Water路線，陷入Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）的可能性極大。一旦局面演變為碉堡戰，那就是被「請君入甕」了。<br />\n香港是動見觀瞻的國際都市，街道星羅棋布，人潮熙攘，因此港青採用Be Water戰術是有效的，也是最令對手頭疼的。對付Be Water，第一就是分化，把勇武派、和理非派拆分，第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/highlight/20191117/IUYMVYNJSBTZCKZAP24QQP6NPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhighlight%2F20191117%2FIUYMVYNJSBTZCKZAP24QQP6NPY%2F&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJyrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=e6e248dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhighlight%2F20191117%2FIUYMVYNJSBTZCKZAP24QQP6NPY%2F&h=4007dd45\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/highlight/20191117/IUYMVYNJSBTZCKZAP24QQP6NPY/</a>"},{"pid":"47ef4e664eeb03625d0606577eaedf3e9e59a140","tid":1729562,"uid":24400,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:26:27.000Z","msg":"11月15日凌晨2時傳來消息，學生已暫離「中大碉堡」，這是正確的決定。然而，北方下來的大內高手還會再放魚餌，估計口味會越來越重，港青可千萬不要再建碉堡。"},{"pid":"b322cb6940da2d43d084579b493c00cd0fdbbf5e","tid":1729562,"uid":24400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:28:46.000Z","msg":"誰偷偷留下負評"},{"pid":"6148e4abdc82cf042da24813ef21f8308d1dd1af","tid":1729562,"uid":24400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:29:17.000Z","msg":"以中文大學為例，坐落其間的HKIX香港互聯網中心，被抗爭運動者視為「必守陣地」，對外通道狹隘（如二號橋），被抗爭者視為「易守難攻」，殊不知此乃「被請君入甕」、一網成擒的誘餌。"},{"pid":"8acb204cfd97b03f1981ced6e7431601a7991f19","tid":1729562,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:30:06.000Z","msg":"守住左垃圾真係把撚"},{"pid":"d0e57edc27aa6bf36d8a57ea495acfb2acf53aa5","tid":1729562,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bab710953b50b9eebcb79f5314b75382a2dbffc","tid":1729562,"uid":24400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:33:18.000Z","msg":"be water"}]}